{"tid":1061235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「蛇竇」樂香園結業在即　店內貼通告：懷緬共處閒話家常","createTime":"2019-03-14T09:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T15:19:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"32298b6aead33c52e9eb387627185f548a1a10b9","tid":1061235,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190314/s00001/cf6806e29d05dbd893f305b26da55508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190314%2Fs00001%2Fcf6806e29d05dbd893f305b26da55508.jpg&h=778b38e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於中環機利文新街的老店「樂香園咖啡室」，宣布將於下周一（18日）結業。不少熟客獲悉後，今日蜂擁到樂香園光顧，表示不捨。樂香園上世紀50年代開業，據說由於地方隱蔽，成為中環打工仔偷懶的地方，俗稱「蛇竇」。數十年來，樂香園以自製麵包和滑蛋叉燒飯聞名，成為街坊和遊客愛到之地。  <br />\n<br />\n樂香園咖啡室的95歲老東主年初離世，接手的老闆鄺潔芳表示工作勞累，趁着為期兩年的租約屆滿，決定結業。 <br />\n<br />\n樂香園在店內貼出結業通知，其中向顧客寫道：<br />\n<br />\n「你們的飲食喜好，常在我心&hellip;&hellip;懷緬共處的時光，閒話家常；永記你們的笑臉，親切溫馨。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190314/s00001/1552548886589/%E3%80%8C%E8%9B%87%E7%AB%87%E3%80%8D%E6%A8%82%E9%A6%99%E5%9C%92%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3-%E5%BA%97%E5%85%A7%E8%B2%BC%E9%80%9A%E5%91%8A-%E6%87%B7%E7%B7%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%99%95%E9%96%92%E8%A9%B1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B8%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190314%2Fs00001%2F1552548886589%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%259B%2587%25E7%25AB%2587%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25A8%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258D%25B3-%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2596%2592%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B8%25B8&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=d16909ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%